---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import CookieConsent from '../components/CookieConsent.astro';
import Button from '../components/Button.astro';
import CtaLink from '../components/CtaLink.astro';

import {
  FileText,
  Shield,
  Info,
  MessageCircle,
  ListChecks,
} from '@lucide/astro';

const pageTitle = 'Non-disclosure agreement (NDA) | Reignite Solutions';
const pageDesc =
  'Use our mutual non-disclosure agreement to protect confidential conversations while we explore your ideas and plans.';
---
<BaseLayout title={pageTitle} description={pageDesc}>
  <Header />

  <main class="text-ink">
    <section class="pt-28 md:pt-32 pb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-surface to-white">
      <div class="container-reignite max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-10 text-left">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <span
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-accent/10 text-accent text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] px-4 py-1 rounded-full"
          >
            Non-Disclosure Agreement
          </span>

          <div class="space-y-4">
            <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-display font-extrabold leading-tight tracking-tight">
              Keep ideas safe while we talk.
            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg text-ink/80">
              This mutual non-disclosure agreement protects confidential information when we explore your product, service or internal
              plans together.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
            <CtaLink
              href="/assets/docs/Reignite-Mutual-NDA.pdf"
              category="NDA"
              label="DOWNLOAD_NDA_PDF"
              download
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-accent text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-md text-base font-semibold hover:bg-black transition"
            >
              <FileText class="w-5 h-5" aria-hidden="true" />
              Download our NDA (PDF)
            </CtaLink>

            <Button
              href="/contact"
              category="NDA_HERO"
              label="TALK_TO_US"
              context="light"
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-3 rounded-md border border-ink/15 text-base font-semibold text-ink hover:border-accent/70 hover:text-accent transition"
            >
              <MessageCircle class="w-5 h-5" aria-hidden="true" />
              Talk to us
            </Button>
          </div>

          <p class="text-sm text-ink/60 max-w-2xl">
            The NDA is written in plain English and set up as a mutual agreement, so it protects both your information and ours.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 bg-ink text-white">
      <div class="container-reignite max-w-5xl space-y-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <ListChecks class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" aria-hidden="true" />
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-display font-semibold">How the NDA works</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
          <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-lg p-6 space-y-3">
            <span
              class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent text-white text-sm font-semibold"
            >
              1
            </span>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Download and fill in</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/80">
              Download the NDA and add your company or trading name and any other details where marked.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-lg p-6 space-y-3">
            <span
              class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent text-white text-sm font-semibold"
            >
              2
            </span>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Send it back to us</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/80">
              Email the completed but unsigned NDA to us so we can review the details and confirm we are happy with them.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-lg p-6 space-y-3">
            <span
              class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent text-white text-sm font-semibold"
            >
              3
            </span>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Sign and countersign</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/80">
              We will sign the agreement and return a copy for you to countersign, so both sides hold the same final version.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 bg-surface">
      <div class="container-reignite max-w-5xl grid gap-12 md:grid-cols-[1.2fr,0.9fr] items-start">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-display font-semibold text-ink">What the NDA actually covers</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-ink/70">
            The NDA is designed for the kind of work we do at Reignite. It covers the information that usually comes up when you are
            shaping or fixing digital products and services.
          </p>

          <ul class="space-y-3 text-base text-ink/80">
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="mt-1 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
              Product, service and roadmap ideas that are not yet public.
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="mt-1 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
              Internal processes, delivery issues and ways of working.
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="mt-1 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
              Commercial details such as pricing, forecasts and budgets.
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="mt-1 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
              Customer, supplier or partner information that is not publicly available.
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="mt-1 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
              Any documents, decks, screenshots or notes you choose to share with us.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-ink/10 p-6 space-y-4 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <Info class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" aria-hidden="true" />
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink">What it does not cover</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink/75">
            The NDA does not treat information as confidential if it was already public, already known to the receiving party, received
            from someone else who was allowed to share it, or developed independently without using confidential information.
          </p>
          <p class="text-xs text-ink/60">
            It is a standard commercial NDA, not a bespoke legal opinion. If you need something tailored to a specific situation, you
            should speak to your legal adviser.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="container-reignite max-w-5xl grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-[1.2fr,0.9fr] items-center">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-display font-semibold text-ink">Not sure if you need an NDA?</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-ink/70">
            If you are unsure whether you need to sign the NDA before talking to us, get in touch. We are happy to work with your own
            agreement if you prefer, or explain how ours works in more detail.
          </p>
          <Button
            href="/contact"
            category="NDA_FOOTER"
            label="ASK_ABOUT_CONFIDENTIALITY"
            context="light"
            variant="primary"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-base"
          >
            <MessageCircle class="w-5 h-5" aria-hidden="true" />
            Ask us about confidentiality
          </Button>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-lg bg-surface border border-ink/10 p-5 text-sm text-ink/75 space-y-3">
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-ink/50">
            Quick recap
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li>• Mutual NDA that protects both sides.</li>
            <li>• Written in clear, plain English.</li>
            <li>• Governed by the laws of England and Wales.</li>
            <li>• Five year term, with trade secrets protected indefinitely.</li>
            <li>• Ready to download and use as part of our work together.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
  <CookieConsent />
</BaseLayout>